                "quality_rating": 1
            },
            {
                "comment": "If you want him to ask you a question, he never tells you if your answer is correct, he only asks the question he wants to ask. This method of learning is of no use to me. Studying with him is a waste of time, and he makes you feel very unsure of yourself, which I really mind.",
                "difficulty_rating": 1,
                "quality_rating": 1
